trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance objektene av et kall til både <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og gi tilgang til sporing dataene beholdes i en SQL-database ved den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>for en bestemt arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance class optimizes its access to the database for its properties, which maintain collections.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance optimaliserer tilgangen til databasen for egenskaper, som har samlinger.

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of activity tracking records that have been sent for this workflow instance to a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService"></xref> database by the run-time tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Henter listen over aktiviteten sporing poster som er sendt til denne arbeidsflytforekomsten til en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService"> </xref> databasen ved kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> is `true`, ActivityEvents contains all activity tracking records sent for this workflow instance up to the current time; if <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> is `false`, ActivityEvents contains the activity tracking records sent up until the last <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A>er `true`, ActivityEvents inneholder alle Aktivitetssporing for poster som er sendt til denne arbeidsflytforekomsten frem til gjeldende dato og klokkeslett; Hvis <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A>er `false`, ActivityEvents inneholder Aktivitetssporing poster sendes opp til siste <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: ActivityEvents contains activity tracking records sent to a database by the run-time tracking infrastructure for this workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: ActivityEvents inneholder poster som er sendt til en database ved kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur for denne arbeidsflytforekomsten Aktivitetssporing.

trans-unit.source: Activity tracking records are sent by the workflow run-time engine tracking infrastructure only when the workflow instance emits an activity status event that corresponds to an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> specified in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for the instance.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet sporing poster sendes av arbeidsflyten kjøretid motoren sporing infrastruktur når arbeidsflytforekomsten avgir en hendelse for aktiviteten status som tilsvarer en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>angitt i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>for forekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"></xref> objects sent for this workflow instance to the tracking database by the run-time tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Listen over <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord"> </xref> objekter som er sendt for denne arbeidsflytforekomsten til databasen for sporing av kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether property data for this <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance"></xref> should be automatically updated when it is accessed.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om egenskapsdata for denne <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance"> </xref> skal oppdateres automatisk når den er tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: To optimize database performance, properties that maintain collections of queried data, such as <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents%2A>, query the database for new elements only when the property is accessed, and the collection for such a property is only updated on an as-required basis when the property is accessed.
trans-unit.target: For å optimalisere ytelsen for databasen, spørres egenskaper som har samlinger av data, for eksempel <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents%2A>, spørre databasen etter nye elementer når egenskapen er tilgjengelig, og samlingen for denne egenskapen bare er oppdatert på basis som kreves når egenskapen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.ActivityEvents%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> class maintains two timestamps for each property: one that indicates the time that tracking data for the collection was last loaded, and another that indicates the last time the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> was refreshed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>klassen opprettholder to tidsstempler for hver egenskap: en som angir tidspunktet når sporing av data for samlingen sist ble lastet inn, og en annen som angir sist i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>ble oppdatert.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: When you get one of the collection properties, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> loads any tracking data that was added to the database between the last time tracking data for the collection was loaded and the last time the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> was refreshed and adds this data to the collection maintained by the property.
trans-unit.target: Når du får en av egenskapene for samling av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>laster inn noen sporing av dataene som ble lagt til i databasen mellom sist sporing av data for samlingen ble lastet inn, og sist i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>ble oppdatert og legger til disse dataene i samlingen vedlikeholdes av egenskapen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: The timestamp that indicates the last time data was loaded for the property is then set to the value of the timestamp that indicates the last refresh.
trans-unit.target: Tidsstempelet som angir siste gang dataene ble lastet inn for egenskapen er deretter satt til verdien for tidsstempelet som angir den siste oppdateringen.

trans-unit.source: If these two timestamps are equal, additional tracking data is not loaded for the property when it is accessed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis disse to tidsstempler er lik, ekstra sporing av data er ikke lastet inn for egenskapen når den er tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: Set AutoRefresh to `true` to perform a refresh every time a collection property is accessed and ensure that the tracking data returned in the collection maintained by that property is always current.
trans-unit.target: Angi AutoRefresh `true` til å utføre en oppdatering hver gang en samling-egenskap er tilgjengelig, og kontroller at sporing dataene som ble returnert i samlingen vedlikeholdes av at egenskapen alltid er oppdatert.

trans-unit.source: If AutoRefresh is `false`, you must call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A> to reset the timestamp that corresponds to the last refresh.
trans-unit.target: Hvis AutoRefresh `false`, må du kaller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>tilbakestille tidsstempelet som tilsvarer den siste oppdateringen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if property data should be automatically refreshed when it is accessed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis egenskapsdata skal oppdateres automatisk når den er åpnet; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> is `true`, InvokedWorkflows contains a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> for each of the workflow instances that has been invoked by this workflow instance up to the current time; if <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> is `false`, InvokedWorkflows contains a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> for each of the workflow instances that has been invoked by this workflow instance up until the last <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the status of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter statusen til arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Status is determined based on the tracking data for the workflow instance, specifically on the workflow tracking records sent by the run-time tracking infrastructure; therefore Status depends, in part, on the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> objects in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Statusen fastsettes basert på dataene sporing for arbeidsflytforekomsten, spesielt for arbeidsflyten sporing poster som er sendt ved kjøretid sporing-infrastruktur; Derfor statusen er avhengig av, i delen, på den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>objekter i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>for arbeidsflytforekomsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> is `true`, WorkflowEvents contains all workflow tracking records sent for this workflow instance up to the current time; if <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> is `false`, WorkflowEvents contains the workflow tracking records sent up until the last <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A>er `true`, WorkflowEvents inneholder alle arbeidsflyten sporing poster som er sendt til denne arbeidsflytforekomsten frem til gjeldende dato og klokkeslett; Hvis <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A>er `false`, WorkflowEvents inneholder arbeidsflyten sporing poster sendes opp til siste <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.Refresh%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.AutoRefresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: WorkflowEvents contains workflow tracking records sent to a database by the run-time tracking infrastructure for this workflow instance.

trans-unit.source: Workflow tracking records are sent by the workflow run-time engine tracking infrastructure only when the workflow instance emits a workflow status event that corresponds to a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> specified in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for the instance.
